We accept the following types of submissions and comments: News : from the original source where possible and with the original title. Stories : reviews, previews, opinion pieces, editorials, podcasts... Retro : the entire history of Nintendo, even before they did videogames Videos : trailers, game analysis Images : official artwork or screenshots for upcoming games Self Posts: open-ended discussion questions, or information
